title: Start Here
overview: Xia Mo, Fang Yuan Jian, Jiang Nan Nan, Cui Jiang Bei and others are a group of young people, who takes scientific and technological innovation, to the next level, and try to improve them, with respected to them fields. Especially Xia Mo, who with her three other friends, opens a company and try to manufacture China's first bipedal humanoid robot. However, does such a scientific geniuses, are able manage to achieve their goal without major perturbations? Especially, that soon, their reasearchers, starts to impact, their personal lives.
